{"tid":800426,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"莫迪歷壓C朗膺最佳 金牌經理人：荒謬！","createTime":"2018-08-31T00:48:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T09:53:51.000Z","uid":153600,"like":9,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"dc8e151270318d996f9dae9a847e41c930413504","tid":800426,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T00:48:28.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=YaD4eHlGJtkOGsmHzZwWNZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=265916ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】基斯坦奴朗拿度的經理人佐治文迪斯炮轟歐洲足協，認為莫迪歷不應該壓倒C朗膺年度最佳，直斥荒謬。<br />\n<br />\n佐治文迪斯接受葡萄牙媒體《Record》訪問時說：「足球是在球場踢的，而基斯坦奴（基斯坦奴朗拿度）是贏家。他攻入15球，帶領皇家馬德里再一次征服歐聯。」<br />\n<br />\n「這是荒謬、可恥，得獎人該毋庸置疑，因為朗拿度是其位置最出色的。」被公認為球壇金牌經理人的文迪斯說來不留情面。<br />\n<br />\n選舉由60位教練及55位歐洲傳媒工作者選出，今夏帶領克羅地亞在世界盃勇奪亞軍的莫迪歷力壓C朗與利物浦的穆罕默德沙拿首奪此獎，其獲得的分數為313，比C朗多90分。<br />\n<br />\n莫迪歷並打破近年C朗與美斯的壟斷，對上一次不是C朗或美斯當選已是2013年，當時由列貝利獲獎。"},{"pid":"803f2ec3f51ca91b29c04c72d4a6be75b83a99c2","tid":800426,"uid":61279,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T01:11:30.000Z","msg":"文迪斯同拉奧拿兩個成日都好似怨婦咁出黎9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c7a462b500738b788fb8ed86707ed1143bbc8d6","tid":800426,"uid":171754,"like":41,"dislike":4,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T01:13:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ced908cab1cf8c601be4756efb98171a1a329314","tid":800426,"uid":34571,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T01:28:28.000Z","msg":"因為朗拿度是其位置最出色的。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為莫迪是其位置最出色的。"},{"pid":"c9fe7d8aa93da3e20d8525b569cb6f0e5a09aa52","tid":800426,"uid":30510,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T01: